(211, '20,D po biro ung online class mas stressed mga students on face to fCe ok un kc my time pero online un time p iba iba tpis un mga teacher give assignments etc anytime khit ntutulog n students tutunig cp kc my new instruction..ok lng daw walang xmas vacation etc pero sna s time n un d rin hectic at less stress lng guv s students pra khit pnu.m enjoy nla ang holiday season .d po porke s haus nag study msarap buhay nla .,Disappointment', 'Others', 50, ''),
