(330, '139,\"Bullshit, are you planning to make us more stressful? BULLSHIT SYSTEM, I sometimes made my assignments 8 to 12 at midnight. I sometimes didn\'t and fucking didn\'t sleep because of that and your planning us suffer? The fuck is wrong with you? SOME STUDENTS HAS GODDAMN MENTAL ISSUES AND YOU ASSHOLE BASICALLY JUST IGNORE THEM\",Anger', 'Others', 50, ''),
(331, '140,I\'m 3 weeks into this online classes and I\'m already regretting it. Tapos ngayon wala pang christmas break?I feel like stabbing myself with a pen right now.,Disappointment', 'Others', 50, ''),
(332, '141,\"Tanginang yan, magisip naman ho kayo kung gaano kabigat saming students \'to. Mas exhausting pa ho tong online class kesa sa face to face. Grabe yung pressure na dala samin tapos tatanggalan niyo pa po kami ng eligibility to enjoy holidays? Jusko, think thrice kasi parang wala po kayo sa katinuan haha\",Anger', 'Upset', 50, ''),
(333, '142,\"Parang walang silbi ang CHED  ABOLISH na yan. Puro NONSENSE naman STATEMENTS nila. Masyadong PLAY SAFE. Ang end, kawawa students, teachers/profs, at parents o mga nagpapaaral.\",Anger', 'Sadness', 50, ''),
(334, '143,\"Greetings with peace!I am Romela Jane Anipot, 19 years old. I am a 2nd year college student taking up Bachelor in Secondary Education, Major in English at University of the Northern Philippines.I am humbly knocking from your kind hearts a small help as I try to raise funds in buying a laptop for my online class.Due to this anxiety-ridden pandemic, I was about to stop for this academic year due to financial matters and we can\'t afford to buy gadgets/electronics for my schooling since the mode of learning was shifted to the online class . My father is only helping his brother in farming while my mother is a housekeeper. I\'m considering myself as the eldest among with my two little sisters who are upcoming Grade 1 and Grade 4. This is because my loving brother passed away last August, 2019 due to an accident at the age of 19.Ever since I was in elementary, I am studying well and wanted to excel in class. In my senior high school life, I graduated with high honors/valedictorian. Honestly, \",Sadness', 'Sadness', 50, ''),
(335, '144,\"I read all the comments and ang daming teacher and students ang nahihirapan tapos sasabihin nyo walang summer walang break? C\'mon isipin nyo yung sitwasyon ng iba! Ang dami ng nababalita na nag suicide at mga nag ddrop na lang kasi di na kaya. \"\"Gusto ko lang po sana ipaalala sainyo ang mga estudyante ay tao rin po hindi robot \"\".\",Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(336, '145,CHED HINDI COVID ANG PAPATAY SA AMIN!!!!!! TSANGGALA ANO NA PILIPINAS!!!!,Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(337, '146,\"Wag naman sanang ganto. Di porket may mga nag enroll na college students this year for the sake of graduating on time e aabusuhin na. Wala nang malamon yung ibang pamilya, pero pinipilit na makapagpaaral ng isang college student sa isip na para makagraduate agad. Nakakanginig ng laman na ganito. Ano yon? Thankful nalang ako na sobrang ok ng school ko, di nila kami pinepressure regarding sa activities, di kami tinatambakan pero wag naman ganyan na pati yung mga araw na pwedeng ipahinga ng estudyante at guro e gagalawin nyo. Kawawa na ang estudyante, lalo na yung mga working students, kawawa din yung mga teacher. Di lang kami estudyante, may ibang gampanin pa kami sa buhay. Bago pa kami maging estudyante o bago pa sila maging guro, anak kami. Kapatid, ina, ama, kaibigan. May buhay kami sa labas ng school. Wag nyo sana yon ipagkait.\",Frustrated', 'Others', 50, ''),
(338, '147,\"Duh, nagsalig ra guru mo kay humana man mog skwela, wala mo ka experience unsa among nabation rung panahona try to put yourself into a student di ba mo kapoyan. We need rest pd uy. Grabe namang inyo na pressure man pd ming mga studyante ani.\",Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(339, '148,Are u out of ur mind u affecting with in this pandemic? Why? Because u don\'t have salary ??? Di nio man lang inisip kapakanan. Ng mga studyante !....,Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(340, '149,\"Sa tiningin nyo Po ba natututo kami Ng maayos? Anong silbi Ng edukasyong ito kung edukasyon din Ang papatay sa Amin bilad na Ang mga mata namin sa cp, ansakit na Ng mga ulo at mata namin ..Wala manlang Po ba kayong konsiderasyon? Gusto nyo pong matuto Ng husto Ang mga magaaral pero hnd nyo ba Alam na maslalo silang tumitigil sa pagaaral Dahl sa mga ginagawa nyo? Hnd Po lahat Ng estudyante parepareho Ang talino .. Hindi nyo Po nakikita Ang hirap namin araw araw maka attend Lang Ng online class na Yan. Sa tingin nyo ba lahat nasa loob Ng bahay nila para mag online class? Hnd dba! Kc kailangan pa naming pumunta dto sa taas Ng bundok para maka internet kc   Wala Pong signal dto sa amin\",Anger', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
(341, '150,SANA MAG PROVIDE DIN YUNG CHED NG LOADKASI YUNG BINIBIGAY SAMING PANG LOAD DAPAT PAMBILI NALANG NG PAGKAIN.,Anger', 'Disgust', 50, ''),
