(559, '368,Is there a significant importance that this kind of education system would help and resolve the problem of our country. #irrelevant. #weneedTRUELEADERS!!,Upset', 'Upset', 50, ''),
(560, '369,\"Do you want to kill the students? First of all you allowed to open the classes for this year without having a proper and effective plan. You didn\'t even conduct a survey among the students and parents if they are agree with this. Students are the one who will study and face the struggles with this kind of system, not you. Every person need to rest, need to breathe. Even if they are just sitting or sleeping the whole day, week or even months. Wake up! THEY are NOT ROBOT!  Do you even know that because of this kind of system many students are having a hard time and even facing an anxiety? Please, don\'t be deaf. Listen to their voice. Listen to their reason and demand. Don\'t make decision without asking them. Because they are the one who\'s experiencing it, not you. BE CONSIDERATE. #AcademicFreeze\",Resentful', 'Upset', 50, ''),
(561, '370,\"izip izip din sir!.notice ko lng sa anak ko.start ng class nya 8am ang tapos nf class nya 5pm. pero innabot na sia ng madaling araw sa pag gawa ng activities nya kasama na lahat ng  assignments bawat subjects, imagine mo sir kung ilang oras naka harap sa laptop amg mga bata? oras ng tulog madaling araw na?! imagine ilang oras sila nakatutok sa radiation ng computer??? araw araw po yun isama na rin ang sunday sa  .... nasa bahay nga pero prang wla din sila sa bahay sa dami ng activities at assignments na binibigay sa knila....kaya izip izip din po!\",Irritated', 'Others', 50, ''),
(562, '371,\"Do these people deserve their positions in the government? If so, why are they being cold hearted and acting as if they are experiencing the same experience as the students today?\",Anger', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
