(564, '373,\"What the fuck? DonÂ’t use this excuse so that students can start another semester after they just ended this semester. This is simply pathetic and subpar to you, which shows that you donÂ’t care about the studentsÂ’ time to actually relax and spend quality time with their family during their break. Even though theyÂ’re home and theyÂ’re taking classes online, that doesnÂ’t mean that theyÂ’re having fun because theyÂ’re at home. So many students want to stop their classes for the time being until the quarantine is over and youÂ’re saying this? How imbecile you are to be in this part of government!\",Disgust', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
