(872, '681,Be considerate sir masyado kang one sided hirap ng Online Class try mo po aral ka ulet tapos CP lang gamit mo at prepaid lng Network mo ang sakit sa ulo ng 6 hours per day take note:hanggang sat and wow just wow sabi nila may modular haha it\'s a prank wala kaming choice lahat kaming college ng BSU lipa sa Btangas Online Class. Try mo sir baka sakaling ma- gets mo we need break kasi kahit Linggo may Ass or Activity parin,Disappointment', 'Others', 50, ''),
(873, '682,\"because students and teachers need a break to celebrate Christmas season with their family*** GANITO PO SANA ANG REASON HINDI BASTA Â“they have to go homeÂ” lang CHED IS DOING THEIR JOB WITHOUT CONSIDERING THAT STUDENTS AND TEACHERS ARE HUMAN TOO AND HAS A DIFFERENT RESPONSIBILITIES ASIDE FROM TEACHING AND STUDYING. EDUCATION IS IMPORTANT BUT FAMILY MATTERS. WAG NYO PO SANANG KAININ ANG ORAS NAMIN DAHIL LANG NAG AARAL KAMI. HOME BASED EDUCATION? SANA NGA PO GANON KADALI MAGKLASE HABANG NASA BAHAY. IH KASI DI MAKA FOCUS KASI WALA PANG SINAING, NAKAKADISTRACT PAPAGALITAN NA NI NANAY KASI DI PA NAKAKAHUGAS NG PINGGAN AATTEND NA AGAD SA ZOOM MEETING. IYAK NG IYAK ANG BUNSONG KAPATID DI MAPATAHAN WALANG MAG AALAGA. PLS CONSIDER DIFFERENT SITUATIONS I UNDERSTAND THAT THIS SITUATION MAKE US SUFFER BUT PLS DO NOT GIVE US UNREASONABLE REASON WE CANT HANDLE IT ANYMORE \",Frustrated', 'Others', 50, ''),
