(891, '700,\"Pwede next yr nlng if normal na Yung face-to-face na... Ok lng Wala Ng summer and Christmas break.... nakaka sakit sa Maya at ulo ang OC class... Nakakagalit ang mahina na signal kuting hangin at ulan walng signal walang kuryente... Tas every day may task Evey subject ... nakakadrain po... Mahirap po kami walay privilege to avail devices, enhance internet connection, tas laki lng load po, tas Wala po ako or kaming protection from bluelight pang bili lng eyewear of blue light screen cover... Pls consider nlng po.... May time for use na mahirap to recover from financial, physical and emotional na didrain napo kami.... EMPHATHY.... We cannot avail what rich can.... Po Hindi po tayo same financial status..and In the midst of crisis affecting all the aspect of humanity especially sa Philippines setting (financially, socially impaired) as the pandemic rises, the psychological phenomenon (stress and depression) is actively on motion now....... I hope na bigyan ng pasin lalo na student na fina\",Anger', 'Sadness', 50, ''),
(892, '701,Sana ikaw nalang mag online class bugok may mga Responsibilidad kame sa Bahay anong akala mo samen pahilata hilata lang kahit studyante kame dumiskarte din kame para mag ka pera BUGOK Ikaw ang kelangan mag aral,Annoyed', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
