(967, '776,\"Konting oras lang ang klase, pero sandamakmak naman ng  iniiwan na gawain, wla ding pahinga, bukod pa ang gawaing bahay,\",Anger', 'Others', 50, ''),
(968, '777,Grabe naman sobrang hard na nga ng Online tapos ayaw nyu pa kami bigyan ng break? So wala pala kayong pakeelam kung mabulag na kami sa kaka aral? Please think this carefully,Disgust', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
(969, '778,\"Kung umakto sila akala mo sila ang mag-aani ng mga kalokohan nila sa future eh. Kailangan ng pahinga ng mga mag-aaral at guro. Just because nasa bahay, wala na silang problema. Well the fact is mas mahirap yung set up nila. Ang dali nyo mag-implement ng kung ano ano kasi wala kayo sa sitwasyon nila at di nyo nakikita paghihirap nila. Aanhin nyo yang academic calendar kung mauubos sa stress at pati kakulangan ng resources ang mga mag-aaral nyo? Nandyan kayo para sa ikabubuti ng madami. Napaghahalataan kayong hindi qualified sa mga posisyon nyo eh.\",Annoyed', 'Annoyed', 50, ''),
(970, '779,ANG TATAHIMIK NIYONG MGA AHENSYA KAYO SA MGA SUICIDE ISSUE REGARDING SA NEW NORMAL CLASSES NGAYON. HINDI PA BA SAPAT YUN NA DAHILAN PARA IHINTO MUNA YUNG KLASE NG ISANG TAON. MAS NAGIGING BOBO KAMI DITO EH.,Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(971, '780,\"wow just wow hoooo.. kumusta naman po kme we need time to relax also, kawawa na utak namin\",Anger', 'Sadness', 50, ''),
(972, '781,\"[Trigger Warning: Suicide]Wake up, DepEd and CHED!A 21-year-old female student, a resident of Zone 1, Sta. Elena, Iriga City, has died of suicide. According to PMSM Edward Dacara, investigator of the case, the parents are clueless that their daughter will die of suicide. According to the interview of Brigada News FM Bicol to the parents, the victim shared no problem aside from her problems in online learning. Aside from gadget-related problems, the victim had difficulties in signal and internet connections [1].This is already the third reported incident of education-relation suicide in Bicol region. Last June 16 and August 15, two students from Sto. Domingo, Albay also died of suicide [2]. These students never choose to end their lives; the government has failed them, the rotten Philippine educational system took their lives away.This frequency of suicide cases related to online classes must be enough for DepEd and CHED to heed the calls of students and teachers. Thus, the recent prono\",Anger', 'Upset', 50, ''),
(973, '782,\"Yes Christmas break gives the opportunity of students to go back home but what is the REASON of going back home? IS TO HAVE TIME FOR OUR FAMILY, BOND WITH YOUR FAMILY, AND TO END THE YEAR WITH A HAPPY THOUGHTS......If there\'s no Christmas break just because we are already at our homes the essence of Christmas is useless because instead of celebrating, we will be busy making requirements......What our students is facing right now is more stressful than ussual\",Sadness', 'Upset', 50, ''),
(974, '783,Wth CHED! This new normal set up of education is more stressful than the face to face classes. Ayaw niyong mahuli kami sa aralin pero ayos lang na magkaproblema kami sa mental health. PUNYETAAAAA!,Anger', 'Disgust', 50, ''),
(975, '784,7 to 5 klase namen halos di na nga kami nakakapag pahinga tapos adjust pa ng mga break.. Wala ba kayong mga anak na nagsusuffer din sa pag o online class maawa naman kayo saming mga mahihirap lang!!!,Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(976, '785,\"Wag niyo sana bigyan pa ng stress ang students and teachers. Lahat naman tayo nagaadjust eh. Ba\'t kami na nag-aaral at pati na rin ang nagtuturo ang kailangan magdusa? At the first place naman, di namin kasalanan ba\'t may COVID-19 right now.\",Anger', 'Others', 50, ''),
(977, '786,Hindi po kami machine na kayang gawin lahat,Resentful', 'Others', 50, ''),
(978, '787,\"BUTI KAPA ALAM MONG FLIXIBLE! KAME KASE HINDI EH!!!! KAHIT NGA NASA BAHAY KAME RAMDAM NAMIN YUNG SCHOOL ATMOSPHERE EH!!!! HALOS SUMAKIT NA NGA ULO NAMIN KAKAISIP NG MGA GAWAIN!!!! DI PO PORKET NASA BAHAY KAME FLEXIBLE NA!!! MAY GINAGAWA DIN PO KAME KASE NGA PO NASA BAHAY KAME HATI YUNG ORAS PO. YUNG IBA NGA PAG GAMIT LANG NG CR AT KUMAIN ANG PAHINGA TAPOS BALIK NA ULEEEE. SIMULA PALANG PERO ILAN NA BA PINANGHINAAN NG LOOB? MADAME NA PO. ANG ONLINE CLASS PO AY PARANG PAGLULUTO NG ITLOG, MASABI LANG NA MAY NALUTO KAHIT MALASADO, IHAHAIN MO.\",Anger', 'Anger', 50, ''),
(979, '788,Kaya nga BREAK tawag dun kasi para may break kami sa school hindi lang para makauwi sa pamilya. Kasi kung uuwi lng sa pamilya ang purpose ng breaks tawag na dun CHRISTMAS HOME.,Dejected', 'Upset', 50, ''),
