(992, '801,\"\"\"Kasi nga, flexible ka. Hindi ka naman every day, 8-9 aattend ng klase? Yng iba, twice a week lang magme-meet because everything now is done on a flexible manner?\"\"  SANA OKAY LANG KAYO, OO MASAYA YAN DUH, SANA OL FLEXIBLE OHO KAYO NA MAG ARAL AH MAY PA FLEXIBLE FLEXIBLE PA KAYONG NALALAMAN need rin namin ng pahinga DI KAMI ROBOT just saying bahala na kayo\",Anger', 'Others', 50, ''),
