(2003, '1812,\"To DepEd Philippines: looks likes this blended learning has been finalized and we parents do not have a choice but to send our children to school even on this trying times (sinabi kong no choice kasi wala naman sigurong parents na gustong mahuli ang anak sa school...). I just hope DepEd Philippines will come up with a detailed program on how this blended learning will happen like how many hours/day does the kids need to be online for online classes, How will the kids/parents get the modules and submit it to the school for checking, How will the children take the monthly exams etc. Thanks!\",Sadness', 'Sadness', 50, ''),
