(4438, '\"I am inviting you to take a online study po tito ulit, para naman po ma try nyo po yung struggle namin as a student  para rin po mahintindihan nyo kung bakit kami puro reklamo specially baryo pa po kami sobrang hirap po humagilap ng internet connection  yung pong pang load po namin is katumbas na po ng 1 Â¼ killo of rice kaso pang isang killo lang talaga aabot yung P50 hirap po kumita ng pera ngayon, kung dito lang po sa baryo maraming tanim na gulay mga tao kaya maraming pwedeng ulamin ehh paano naman po yung mga taga syudad lahat nalang binibili nila, tapos christmass break na ngalang po yung makakapag-pabawas ng gastusin para sa online class gusto nyo pa po ata maalis  kahit wala ng handa handa sa pasko basta kumpleto pamilya masaya na po nun.\"', 'Sadness', 52, ''),
(4439, '\"So you\'re saying that the holidays only existed becaude students needs to go home to their homes to celebrate the events? I thought CHED is supposed to be a higher education management. But what the hell am I reading? If this is how we should function as the students/teachers of this country, it should worry you. All your personnels have families. If we cannot have the break to feel mentally safe and rested, then we should expect the same from ALL OF YOU in that sector. If we must give ours, please do yours. I hope I don\'t see pictures of celebrations or yall Im losing my shit over this school calendar. It feels more like education is not respected and appreciated. If we are just passing for the sake of ending this semester and paying the tuitions on time, we should least GET BENEFIT FROM IT.\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4440, 'Soooo Di na din uso Christmas sainyo? Di na din uso pahinga sainyo? Palibhasa kasi di kayo napapagod sa kakanakaw ng pera para sa napakadissapointing services ninyo. Tapos tatanggalan niyo kami ng Christmas break. Mga walang hiya kayong hayop kayo', 'Anger', 52, ''),
(4441, 'If you are going to take away students\' and teachers\' break. Might as well reduce the months of having a class. But just WTF is going on with your minds? Are you saying that we are going to ignore some traditions just for this fucked up class? Being in our homes does not mean we can spend a lot of times with our family if you are forcing us to practice this nonsense. You call this quality education? I didn\'t the meaning of quality is forcing what you want to achieve. ', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4442, 'Hoy! Napaka hirap na ng online learning puro pagawa ang prof! Tapos di nio pa kami pag papahingahin! Hindi kami robot! Nasisiraan na ako ng ulo! Nagagalit na ako! Grrrrr! Raarrrrrrrr! #Isipisipdindinakayonagiisipikayokayailagaynaminsasitwasyonnaminorngibananagdadatalangwalangwaypay', 'Anger', 52, ''),
