(4456, '\"this is the most stupidest bullshit I\'ve ever seen done, wtf are you talking about \"\"pag break, pinauuwi\"\", are you that fucking retarded, first of all a break is meant to help a student relax after an exam or even after schools, it isn\'t just meant for the student to go home, that part of your line obviously shows how mentally inept you are. second, even if they only meet for twice a week at minimum (which I doubt they actually do but you do you), the amount of Homeworks and performance task they can make up for all that lost time which they can also use to SELF STUDY, wow it\'s like that word doesn\'t exist for you to think students don\'t self study and need to always be in class to be productive. another thing, if you even use the excuse of \"\"yeah but look at us in the working class\"\" then I\'ve completely lost hope in you having a functioning brain, you guys get paid, we pay YOU to educate us, to remove breaks just because you don\'t get as much break time is the equivalent of an adult tak\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4457, 'hey! r u fucking kidding me? just a few weeks and we already need a break coz were fucking mentally and physically tired and yet? ur thinking or removing our only time to take a rest? u said that were already home? nope. like me. other students are living on a boarding house/apartments just to have a good internet connection before our home/location doesn\'t have any signal. our expenses is already doubled just to keep up with the previlaged. We need a break. Can\'t you see? are the government blind? We are fucking tired. U want to keep up with the other nations? then go and fucking migrate live on that fucking place. we don\'t need leaders who don\'t fucking care of it\'s people. We\'re all tired. aint eating a 3 times a day meal because we\'re saving money to live the next day. we still have expenses to pay. wake up man.', 'Others', 52, ''),
