(4513, '\"What the. Just because we\'re inside our homes doesn\'t mean we\'re free all the time. We have chores, dreams we could achieve, talents that we\'re polishing. Our home isn\'t just some chill and lazy place, we also have work within these walls. If seasonal breaks will be removed, then self-time would be more limited unlike now, and the negative atmosphere that surrounds most people today might be more dense than usual.\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4514, '\"Kailan kaya mauunawaan ng CHED na ang pagiging flexible sa online class ay hindi lang patungkol sa time availability ng studyante? Hindi lahat flexible dahil hindi lahat may materials na gagamitin, hindi lahat kaya mag self study, hindi lahat nakakacope up, hindi lahat may stable na internet, hindi lahat may pang load araw araw, hindi lahat priveledge. Hay \"', 'Others', 52, ''),
