(4564, 'Kahit Summer Break nlng alisin since sanay na kami mag-aral kahit summer pero yung Christmas break yun nlng yung family time namin.. Di niyo ba maisip na kahit online class kami mas kinukuha pa rin nito ung time namin na halos di na kami makatayo sa upuan namin', 'Annoyed', 52, ''),
(4565, '\"HUH  pathetic ,CHED di na kau nag-iisip ng maayos.they are entitled for a break.you are right they are just home because of the online class but havent you asked them if they are still ok with this new normal.daming struggle with the workloads given .if ever they will opt for the usual class .nakababad cla ng how many hours sa laptop so vulnerable sa radiation and sakit ng ulo.  di naman kasalanan na magkaroon ng pandemic.dont you know the meaning of BREAK?how about you ?will you do the same since you are working from home? mag isip naman po!\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4566, '\"Mabuti sana kung effective ang online class kaso hindi eh. Halos lahat ng estudyante nahihirapan na sa online class. Puro gawain lang pinapagawa niyo sa amin at wala din kaming natututunan. Siguro mararamdam niyo paghihirap namin kung nagpalit tayo ng pwesto. Hindi na talaga ito nakakatuwa. Madaming estudyante ang nagbibigay ng opinions nila sa \"\"New normal\"\" na ito kaso walang aksyon din. Iniisip lamang ang sarili bago ang iba\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4567, '\"Be considerate please CHED, not all students are with their families nor others are there in the places where signals are only accessible. Some are missing their love ones at home but because of poor connections on required internet to study, some and most of students are striving too hard because of this new strategy of learning. Some of others are with their homes with net and very comfortable with their companions, but the questions are, are they really have bonding even at once  at meal? Or even happy? Parents are in their fields of works tho.\"', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(4568, '\"Waw, i have No right to speak like the others kasi di naman ako babad mag aral. Pero ibang usapan na ung samin nyo ipapasa ung burden na hindi nyo kaya solusyunan. GINUSTO ba namin mag ka pandemic and yet some effects of Government incompetence handling this pandemic will be passed on us. Yo, that\'s true we are not going to school 8-9hrs but Tf you think we are chillin? Mas madalas pa kami magkamustahan magka kaklase kung kamusta ung mga activity e. I have no problem sa school ko because they handle the situation well..Pero we are not in the same place. HINDI TAYO PAREPAREHAS lalo na pag dating sa Learning Capability at social status. Sa totoo lang itong online class it is just to COMPLY at hindi lahat natututo. TAPOS GUSTO NYO PA WALANG BREAK HAHAHA bakit kami mag susuffer sa wrong decision making nyo. Ang problema.kasi sainyo HINDI nyo PINAKIKINGGAN ung mga hinaing ng tao. Isipin mo maigi We are at home pero parang wala lang din kami kasi tutok sa online class at activity.Christmas B\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4569, '\"Hays,wala ba silang common sense,breaks are supposed to ease the tension from school\"', 'Disgust', 52, ''),
(4570, '\"Gosh where is his brain??? Eaten by covid19???Even teachers need to take a break...College faculty (like me) needs a break... not to mention the fact that I have not received any salary because I\'m a non-tenured faculty and even the semester started  I (we) have already received tasks and started working.While, some are receiving their paychecks with less work and could not even cut the culture of delaying salaries.\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4571, '\"Are we really at \"\"home?\"\" If not going out of our bedrooms, seeing and talking with our families rarely, and experiencing anxiety, panic, and stress brought by the schools to our houses is how you define a \"\"home.\"\" Then, I guess I\'ve been wrong all my life for thinking that a HOME is where I find peace and tranquility.\"', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(4572, 'The DepEd should too. Students need to cope up with the academic calendar.', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(4573, 'What a stupid and ignorant government policy if you can\'t give us the #AcademicFreeze that we asking and you\'ll also deny student break Christmas/Summer then do a lot of free mass testing so the students can easily go back in standard way of learning and everyone is satisfied.', 'Annoyed', 52, ''),
