(4620, 'Is there a significant importance that this kind of education system would help and resolve the problem of our country. #irrelevant. #weneedTRUELEADERS!!', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(4621, '\"Do you want to kill the students? First of all you allowed to open the classes for this year without having a proper and effective plan. You didn\'t even conduct a survey among the students and parents if they are agree with this. Students are the one who will study and face the struggles with this kind of system, not you. Every person need to rest, need to breathe. Even if they are just sitting or sleeping the whole day, week or even months. Wake up! THEY are NOT ROBOT!  Do you even know that because of this kind of system many students are having a hard time and even facing an anxiety? Please, don\'t be deaf. Listen to their voice. Listen to their reason and demand. Don\'t make decision without asking them. Because they are the one who\'s experiencing it, not you. BE CONSIDERATE. #AcademicFreeze\"', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(4622, '\"izip izip din sir!.notice ko lng sa anak ko.start ng class nya 8am ang tapos nf class nya 5pm. pero innabot na sia ng madaling araw sa pag gawa ng activities nya kasama na lahat ng  assignments bawat subjects, imagine mo sir kung ilang oras naka harap sa laptop amg mga bata? oras ng tulog madaling araw na?! imagine ilang oras sila nakatutok sa radiation ng computer??? araw araw po yun isama na rin ang sunday sa  .... nasa bahay nga pero prang wla din sila sa bahay sa dami ng activities at assignments na binibigay sa knila....kaya izip izip din po!\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4623, '\"Do these people deserve their positions in the government? If so, why are they being cold hearted and acting as if they are experiencing the same experience as the students today?\"', 'Annoyed', 52, ''),
(4624, 'Hahahah well oks lang naman ehh kung maayos internet at mabilis at ska kumpleto lahat ng gamit ng bawat isa diba ?? Ano sa tingin mo mayaman ba lahat para maka pag provide ng mga ganyan ?? Diba hindi ?? Nag struggle sila sa PAG HAHANAP KUNG SAAN MAKAKAKUHA NG MGA GADGETS AT INTERNET ..... TAPOS WALA PANG BREAK ??? ANO SA TINGIN NINYO ROBOT KAMI ??????? MADAMI DIN KAMING NAHIHIRAPAN HINDI LANG KAYO PARE PAREHAS LANG NAMAN DIBA ?? INIISIP NIYO KUNG PAANO KAMI MAKAKAPAG TULOY NANG KLASE PERO NAISIP NIYO BA YUNG WALANG MGA PERA AT MGA MAAYOS NA CELLPHONE ?? SAYANG NAMAN YUNG NAIISIP NIYO KUNG DI RIN NAMAN LAHAT NAKAKASABAY DIBA ?? SAYANG YUNG PANAHON OO TAMA KAYO PERO SAYANG DIN NAMAN YUNG PANAHON NUNG HINDI MAKAKASABAY DIBA ??   ANO BA GUSTO NIYO ????? SANA NAMAN MABIGYAN LANG NANG LINAW KASE HINDI LAHAT MAY KAYA HINDI LAHAT MERING GADGETS NA MAGAGAMIT PARA SA ONLINE CLASS NILA HINDI LAHAT MAY WIFI SA KANI KANILANG BAHAY.... MAY DATA NGA PERO GASTOS DIN SA PERA KELANGAN LAGI KANG MAY LOAD', 'Others', 52, ''),
(4625, '\"What the fuck? Donâ€™t use this excuse so that students can start another semester after they just ended this semester. This is simply pathetic and subpar to you, which shows that you donâ€™t care about the studentsâ€™ time to actually relax and spend quality time with their family during their break. Even though theyâ€™re home and theyâ€™re taking classes online, that doesnâ€™t mean that theyâ€™re having fun because theyâ€™re at home. So many students want to stop their classes for the time being until the quarantine is over and youâ€™re saying this? How imbecile you are to be in this part of government!\"', 'Annoyed', 52, ''),
