(4634, '\"What I just wanted to say sir is \'IKAW NALANG SKWELA!\' Our classhours has limit, yes. But let us just feel the essence of christmas and summer vacation. Students must not get stressed kasi it may lead to anxiety and depression. Flexible naman kami sir pero mahirap din naman kasi minsan pag kalaban mo yung classworks na nagsasabayan ng deadline. Let us breathe for the mean time, di pwes sa bahay lang kami nag-aaral eh wala na kaming role bilang isang anak. Ano yun? During christmas, new year and summer na supposed vacatio namin, lahat ng students stress at nagkakakanda kuba - kuba na sa pagpasa ng requirements? Lmao.\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
