(5058, 'Di niyo naman po kasi nararanasan ang hirap na kinahaharap ng mga estudyante at mga guro.', 'Anger', 52, ''),
(5059, '\"\"\"Hindi naman everyday 8-9 a-attend ng klase\"\" Opo. Pero yung activities kulang 24 hrs sa pag gawa. Ang galing n\'yo po. Sana wala rin kayong day-off. Kasi nasa bahay lang naman po kayo\"', 'Anger', 52, ''),
(5060, '\"ANONG TWICE A WEEK. yung kapatid ko EVERYDAY 5 days a week, tapos weekend nauubos sa requirements, quiz at exam. isip isip libre lang naman\"', 'Others', 52, ''),
(5061, 'Don\'t blame us students from this generation if we are not molded according to your visions', 'Upset', 52, ''),
(5062, '\"Despite the struggles and complaints of  students abt online class, how it affects  their mental health. Even some students selling nudes for academic purposes in this online set up, you still turn blind eye and deaf to the shouts of students and teachers. Where\'s the empathy CHED? alam ko namang bulok na dati ang sistema natin pero mas pinatunayan niyo lang na mas may ibubulok pa nga. No breaks? What are we then? Robot? Dude, this is not cool.Ligtasbalikeskwela sana at mass testing unahin\"', 'Others', 52, '');
