(5074, '\"wait,what?? \"\"they\'re already at home\"\"??????? eh pano po kaming nag aaral malayo sa kanya kanyang pamilya??i mean,nag rerent ng boarding house? alam nyo ba yon? sa tingin ko hindi.....kaya po kami nag bobording/nagrerent ng bording house na malayo sa amin kasi po doon po sa amin,walang signal,walang koneksyon sa internet.....mas pinili po naming mag enrol pa din kc gusto namin makapag aral kahit na alam naming madami kaming isasakripisyo financially...tang inang sistemang to..di na kau nakakatulong,imbes na hikayatin nio kaming magpatuloy sa pag aaral eh parang dinadagdagan nio pa problema....just admit it......YOU ARE NOT READY!!! WE ARE ALL NOT READY!!!!!!!\"', 'Anger', 52, ''),
(5075, 'Di nyo ba na iitindihan na hihirapan po kami', 'Anger', 52, ''),
(5076, '\"If you can\'t give us the #AcademicFreeze that we ask and you\'ll also deny us the Christmas/Summer break that we need, then help us urge this government to execute #FreeMassTesting, so we can have #LigtasBalikEskwela and everyone is satisfied. \"', 'Annoyed', 52, ''),
(5077, 'Ilan pa kaya mamatay para lang bigyan ng pahinga ang mga student. Kasi ho ako pagod na din', 'Others', 52, ''),
