(8435, '\"YOU ARE TREATING US AS IF WE HAVE NO CONTROL IN OURSELVES! HINDI NA KAMI BATA CHED! YOU DONT HAVE TO CONFINE US WITH THIS \"\"EDUCATIONAL SYSTEM\"\" YOU ARE HAVING. MENTAL ILLNESS YUNG INIIWASAN NAMIN KAYA KAMI DUMADAING NA MAG ACADEMIC FREEZE! NOT EVERYONE IS CAPABLE! AT YUNG SINAMPAL NYO SAAMIN NA 24M already enrolled STUDENTS, MOST OF THEM NAPILITAN LANG I\'M TELLING YOU! DAHIL MAY HINAHABOL NA SCHOLARSHIP AND VOUCHERS. YOU LEAVE THEM NO CHOICE. STOP TRYING TO MANIPULATE US. STUDENT\'S AREN\'T LEARNING ANYMORE! \"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
