(8597, '\"This cannot help students and also parents.We should consider our time and bond with our family especially this season of Christmas,because life is too short.Open up you hearts and mind Ched because students or I should say many students are suffering with this kind of policies, they are committing suicide due to stress and anxiety attacks also teachers,guardian or parents can be stress because imstead of buying the money for their food they use the money on load.This kind of policies canâ€™t prepare us in the future.\"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
