(8649, '\"We have break already okay so we must consider that  thing because we\'re a students, our break is enough, like from the end of last school year, 3 months  is not a break for everyone? I don\'t  think so. Like the adjustments said already, we\'re  in our house maybe a week for celebrating Christmas is too much, because we need tobe flexible, remember? even we\'re  not wanting  it, we cares because  we\'re suffering but, are just we, only a students? Also the teachers and the government are not yet ready for it too. They need to work too maybe we didn\'t  know if they have a break when  we having already.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8650, 'Bahalag wala nalang muy kaluoy namung mga students sa mga teachers nalang po. They deserve a REST. â˜ºï¸', 'Sadness', 53, ''),
(8651, '\"MAG FACE-TO-FACE NALANG SIGURO TA SIR UY!!! GISAYUNAN UROY MO DA. NAKA IMPLEMENT LAGI UG \"\"FLEXIBLE MODE OF LEARNINGS\"\" KUNO, WA HUNA HUNAA NA NAA PA DIAY NAG LISOD. HAHAHAHAHAHA PA TILAWA SAG PAHULAY ANG MGA PROFESSORS SIR UY! O DI KAYA, MOSUGOT MI DI MI MAG SUMMER UG CHRISTMAS PERO IKAW TUDLO SAMOA TANAN. BE FLEXIBLE HA, DAPAT MAMANAGE NMO TANAAN STUDENTS FROM LUZON TO MINDANAO. Kalagot! \"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8652, 'Nakikipag kompetensya kasi sa ibang bansa eh Alam naman na third world country tayu....Kung Wala Lang sanang corruption... Na nagaganap edi Sana masaya Ang Pilipinas ngayun at tsaka esrudyante Lang kami kailangan Rin namin Ng pahinga.', 'Others', 53, ''),
