(8667, 'Hear the voice of students naman po wag po padalos dalos and lahat ng students are now struggling about this situation also they need to rest anong akala niyo sa mga students? Robot? We\'re still a HUMANS Sir! And yes! We do not attend classes for 8-9 but we are doing our modules or activities  24/7 and some students  forget to eat and sleep on time! Sana naman aware kayo sa mental health ng mga students! ', 'Upset', 53, ''),
