(8689, 'No they\'re at their house but you\'ll never call it HOME kung pagkakaitan nyo sila/kami ng spare time to spend for ourselves o kaya sa pamilya stress ba naman ipang Noche Buena mo edi HO HO HO THANKS MR.PROSPERO', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8690, '\"Iâ€™m starting to believe more and more that the â€œheadsâ€ of the educational sector of the government never went to school, or are just archaic to realize how their decisions lack basic common sense. \"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8691, '\"What I just wanted to say sir is \'IKAW NALANG SKWELA!\' Our classhours has limit, yes. But let us just feel the essence of christmas and summer vacation. Students must not get stressed kasi it may lead to anxiety and depression. Flexible naman kami sir pero mahirap din naman kasi minsan pag kalaban mo yung classworks na nagsasabayan ng deadline. Let us breathe for the mean time, di pwes sa bahay lang kami nag-aaral eh wala na kaming role bilang isang anak. Ano yun? During christmas, new year and summer na supposed vacatio namin, lahat ng students stress at nagkakakanda kuba - kuba na sa pagpasa ng requirements? Lmao.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8692, '\"Hindi na nga po ready for online class, pati ba naman christmas break pinagkait pa yun nalang yung tingin kong pahinga ng nga estudyante.Hays goodluck mental health \"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8693, 'Huwaw .. Students are not robots... This new normal online classes itself is too tiring for the eyes.. Imagine having classes frm 7am to 5pm.. An hr brk Lang.. Minsan ultimo brk kinukuha p ng prof s overtym.iba ang physical class sa nktituk ka Lang sa monitor ng laptop MO.. Saturday and Sunday ng aaral pa din at may tinatapos na reports handouts etc.. Napaapgod din sila.. For Pete\'s sake..', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
