(8698, '\"Hahaha flexible daw. Ang nabago lang naman is hindi na kami pumupunta ng school para mag intay kung may klase oh wala, pero yung activity loads same pa din mas dumami pa nga. Aminin ko din kahit malakas signal ng phone ko mahirap pa din makinig pag sa online nagtuturo ang prof kase limited lang talaga ang matutunan namin. Kaya wag nyong sabihin na flexible ang system ng pag aaral ngayon. Baka pasulatin ko kayo ng cases sa papel tapos pipicturan and isesend sa prof kahit pwede naman na sa Microsoft/WPS gawin. And yung groupings sa thesis? Yes sounds easy right? Kase groupings pero pag di mo naman kaharap yung groupmates mo and hirap mag brainstorming and magshare ng thoughts and Ideas about sa gagawin nyo, so anong flexible don ha #CHed?Kami na nga yung nag adjust sa learning system kahit mahirap. kami din yung magbabayad pa ng tuition/token fee kahit wala kami sa school physically to study. Then mag aadjust ulit kami dahil i aadjust nyo yung school calendar at tatanggalan kami ng break\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8699, 'WOW SANA NAG HINGI MUNA KAYO NG OPINYON NAMIN HINDI DESISYON AGAD TAENA KAYO MAG ARAL AH! KAINIS KAYO SABIHIN NATING NASA BAHAY LANG PERO TAO RIN KAMI PUNYETA GRR!!#AcademicFreezeNow', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
(8700, '\"Please be considerate with the students and to the teachers naman po. We are all struggling kasi ang hirap sa online class especially if mahina yung connection nyo. And not all people have there internet connection. Everyday kami (students) puyat na dahil lang sa mga assignments. We also need a break, not just for the students but for the teachers also.\"', 'Sadness', 53, ''),
(8701, '\"Insensitive! You have to hear us as well. Our time at home are all consumed. For a week\'s worksheets seem like we\'re making research sample and somehow a project making because the workloads are too heavy! Our time even time for ourselves are consumed for making assignments. More than 10 files uploaded and each doesn\'t have one page to be answered!! We are physically, mentally and emotionally draining! We are not learning anymore!  We\'re now rushing to finish activities. Wake up CHED and DepEd  open your eyes! There are a lot of students at your back kneeling down not to beg but because of losing energy. I swear that this year will be forgotten\"', 'Outraged', 53, ''),
