(8740, 'honestly this isnâ€™t about education anymore  if you ask me this is torture ang hirap gumising ng maaga para lang sa unstable na net na at the end of the day wala kang natutunan at all through out the day nilalabanan yung mo antok mo gawa nang awkward silence ng online class hindi sya mahirap', 'Others', 53, ''),
