(8778, 'Sasabihin dumaan na kami sa pagiging estudyante try nyo mag online class sa panahon nyo para maintindihan nyo sila', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
(8779, '\"Well if CHED won\'t hear us, I pray that our schools will hear, feel and see us.\"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8780, '\"GRABE NAMAN PO YUN, WALA NA PO BA KAYONG AWA SA MGA ESTUDYANTE AT MGA GURO ?? HINDI PABA KAYO NAKOKONSENSYA SA MGA NAG SUICIDE DAHIL SA ONLINE CLASS ? YUNG IBA WALANG INTERNET, YUNG IBA WALANG GADGETS, YUNG IBA MAY INTERNET MABAGAL NAMAN SANA NMAN MAAWA KAYO. WHAT IF MAGPALIT TAYO NG SITWASYON ANO PO KAYANG MARARAMDAMAN NIYO? ANO BA HINAHABOL NIYO PERA ? TANGINA NAHIHIRAPAN NA YUNG MGA TEACHERS OHH, AKO PO INAAMIN KONA TAMAD AKO PUMASOK NOON, PERO SA SITWASYON NGAYON MAS TATAMARIN KA EH.. #AcademicFreezeNow\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8781, '\"srsly?! kaming mga estudyante yung mga main subjects sa usapan na yan tas hindi nyo man lang papakinggan yung mga say namen abt sa school year na to? kasalanan ba namen nagka-covid kaya pinapahirapan niyo kami sa studies namen ngayon isa lang masasabi ko \"\"ang babaho nyooo\"\"\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8782, 'Nagpapasa nalang naman ng mga act. para masabing may natutunan', 'Sadness', 53, ''),
(8783, '\"Many still come and stay in the city to have decent internet, my girlfriend does that. She still left home for online class.\"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8784, '\"Yes we dont attend classes 8-9 hours but were doing modules 24/7 all i can say is, this guy is heartless He doesnt know what students are going through. With this new norm in schooling, working students like me who have lost a job are having problems financially we cannot cope up with the high demands of the online classes. Interms of loads and gadgets if you make the online classes seven days a week what would happen to students like me, When in fact i dont even know where i would get the load for my online classes this week. I dont know if my phone will still work in the coming days because the memory is already full because of the modules and assessments thats what people do when they dont experience what others does. Act like a boss play like a boss. Care not of something they dont experience because its not them who are suffering but us.\"', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
(8785, '\"Kabataan daw ang pag asa ng bayan, pero bakit hindi niyo kami pinapakinggan?\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8786, '\"Aren\'t we too globally competitive for not allowing students to have their break? Haven\'t you consider their emotional and mental state? You demand us for flexibility and yet you cannot provide for every student\'s needs knowing that we\'re not on the same page.A lot of us-students are already struggling for this \"\"new normal\"\" system. Majority are working to earn to provide for school expenses. A little break wouldn\'t hurt, please think and decide whats best for the people.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8787, 'This kind of people doesn\'t care about  us students and teachers palibhasa hindi Kasi nila nararanasan yung mga nararanasan natin. We also need a rest. Seriously this things sucks.', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8788, 'Aba give them a break dn nman kht Pano kawawa nman dn mga students lutong luto ang utak nila..ngayon n nga lng eh puro home work CLA instead of more in discussion..Baka nman s depression bumagsak mga students Nyan isip isip dn nmn ho..', 'Fear', 53, ''),
(8789, 'You\'re a complete douchebag if you think we students don\'t need a break from all the stress and weariness that we are experiencing from online learning. ', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8790, '\"Isa nanamang bonak ng ahinsya chairman ng commission on higher education pero Wala namang utak, kung Hindi ka nahihirapan sa buhay mo eh kami po hirap kami sa buhay namin wag kana dumagdag sa stress namin bonak ka\"', 'Outraged', 53, ''),
(8791, 'Ayusin niyo muna internet connection namin tangina niyo di pwedeng si liza lang may 300mbps. ', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8792, 'You know  the management is bad when even the educational sector of the gov proposes this kind of BS. It is not our fault that the gov did not take covid seriously as it was starting out while other countries prepared so well that they dont have a single case of it now. No other country in this world would eradicate academic breaks and holidays because of this pandemic.   The audacity and stupidity is overwhelming.', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8793, '\"Y\'all don\'t wanna be left behind by other countries so you\'ll just let the student suffer. Wtf, people. DON\'T FUCKING LET THE STUDENTS SUFFER!!!!!!!!! SUMISIGAW NG ACADEMIC FREEZE \'YAN IBIBIGAY N\'YO?! HINDI N\'YO BA NABALITAAN? OR YOU JUST DON\'T CARE ABOUT THOSE STUDENTS WHO COMMIT SUICIDE?! WHAT A SHAME TO ALL OF  YOU.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8794, 'Parang gusto kona talagang wagna monang Magaral', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8795, '\"You\'re Being inconsiderate. I have a friend she already have a child and she\'s in 3rd year college now, she\'s also a online seller. Ayaw niya mag stop kasi sayang daw yung taon tsaka ayaw niya mapag iwanan kung hindi pa kami mag papalit palitan sa pag bantay sa baby niya nainaanak namin hindi siya makakapag online class ng maayos. Tas gusto nyo pang agawin yung holidays na magsisilbing pahinga nalang niya.Seriously nawawalan na ng boses ang kabataan.Sabi ni Dr. Jose Rizal \"\"Kabataan ang pag asa ng bayan\"\" pero paano kung ang kabataan hindi na umabot sa kinabukasan dahil sa stress at depression na dala ng Online Class.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
(8796, '\"Utak niyo may ubo, kailangan din namin ng break kahit nasa bahay na kami wag kayong ano jan. Kahit tanggalin niyo pa ang summer break, hindi pa rin nito binabago ang katotohanan na walang natututunan ang mga estudyante.\"', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
(8797, '\"Parents need to step in. If they see that online classes are not suitable for their children anymore and its not healthy for their children anymore, then they can choose to have their children Stop for this year. Stop sending their children to school. Hindi naman masama na tumigil ng isang taon e. Kung hindi kayang ibigay ng gobyerno ang #AcademicFreeze, then parents should decide for their children. They should decide not to send their kids to school if they think its not healthy for their children anymore. This is called responsible parenting #justsaying\"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8798, '\"If I am a parent of a old-enough-to-be-a-student, i\'ll not enroll him for this year. Specially how the DEPED AND CHED works now.Parents, should be responsible for learning of their kids at least this year.It\'s a different story if college level or masteral since they\'ll know much how to keep theirselves safe in times like this(though no one is spared from the virus).This may not apply to everyone, again \"\"if am a parent of a old-enough-to-be-a-student kid.\"\"\"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8799, '\"Taena CHED gusto ko nalang umiyak. Di naman kame ganon katambak sa gawain kase napakaunderstanding ng mga prof namen. Pero andame ng students na naghinto, and worst may mga nagsuicide na dahil sa burden ng online class na to. BAKET KAYO GANYAN?\"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8800, '\" If we can\'t stop the gov\'t to academic freeze, what if tayo ang magpastop? What I mean is magkaisa ang lahat ng student na wag mag enroll? Baka sa pamamagitan nun eh mapahayag ng Gov\'t and academic freeze kasi feel ko malalakas loob nila kasi marami pa rin na student ang nag eenroll eh kaya pinagpapatuloy nila hehehe.. Just my opinion.\"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8801, '\"Baka gusto niyo po pakita schedule namin? Walanjo sabado na nga lang wala kaming pasok pero dami naman nakatambak samin na gawain kahit gawin namin ng maaga pa sa deadline  mentally and physically tired na kame 3weeks of classes palang  and alam namin yung sacrifice rin ng mga prof samin kada gawa ng ppt or mga quizzes pero wala malapit na kaming sumuko sa sobrang daming activities, assignment \"', 'Annoyed', 53, ''),
(8802, 'twice a week daw halatang walang alam sa ganap sa online class pota dag dag mopa yung mga assignment na sabaysabay pati reporting tas tamang self study kapa putaaaaa', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8803, 'Nag iisip ba si Chairman De Vera ng maayos? Ano ba tingin niya may  26 units per sem kahit dalawang meeting lang per week sandamakmak naman ang activities pano magiging flexible manner yon?  Kahit di nyo na dinggin yung acad freeze wag nyo lang iextend hanggang sunday ang pasok utang na loob hindi lahat ng student may pang load ng  straight 7 days para sa mga walang internet connection ', 'Anger', 53, '');
