(8830, '\"Here\'s the reason why CHED cannot implement the academic freeze, because when you allow the stop of classes money will also stop . Different academic year is different budget, so no more money to corrupt, the money flows is also affected and other agencies or industry. # my personal opinions only.\"', 'Upset', 53, ''),
(8831, '\"Toxic government trait :\"\"pag bata ka pa walang silbe ang ideya mo!\"\"\"', 'Anger', 53, ''),
(8832, '\"i chose not to enroll online classes, why?? because i only have phone na magagamit, old model, 16gb only and couldnt cater to install more apps dahil updated na lahat ng mga built-in apps!!  no laptops, walang pang load sa wifi! kung may wifi man mahina ang signal, nakakastress, nakakadepress, sakit sa mata at ulo, may trabaho pa.sa bahay dahil kailangan tulungan ang magulang, walang pera!! tas kung makapagsalita ka parang lahat kaming estudyante mayayaman na maka afford.bumili ng bagong gadgets!! ano tayo? america? ano gusto mo umutang kami ng gadgets?? what for, online classes na wlaa namang matutunan?? ano ba talaga utak mo sir?\"', 'Sadness', 53, ''),
(8833, 'Bkt nakikita nio ba situation nameng mga magaaral? And besides Kau ba magaaral? Lalo na kaming mga Med course more on duty/hospital base kami puwede mo bang turukan gadgets mo? Haysss at hnd kami robot napapagod ren kami...', 'Outraged', 53, ''),
(8834, 'Dude u making me angry! Yes you got a point! But may I just remind you that we are not robots! We also need a break!  Youâ€™re torturing us physically and mentally! Please consider also our mental health! Weâ€™re having a hardtime fixing our schedules tapos walang pang break??!! Fudge! Hear our mourns!Fix your decisions you heartless and brainless leaders!!! ', 'Others', 53, ''),
