(10326, '\"It seems to me you are really pushing for the fulfillment of your mandate in helping to nurture a complete and whole individual You mention that otherwise, they will become robots. With all due respect po, isusulong nyo po ng husto yang gusto nyong mangyari, para hindi maging parang robot ang mga bata, pero namatay naman sila dahil kinapitan ng virus. Ano po ang saysay nun? So, you mean you\'d rather put to risk the lives of the children just to meet your goal? Kahit po on a limited scale, it doesn\'t make sense. People were requested/urged/advised to stay home to prevent the spread of the virus, so why will you still enforce this mandate na papasukin ang mga bata? Please be more considerate naman po. Need po talaga ng mga bata ang human interaction outside their home, pero not at this time po. Nakamamatay po ito, di na mababalik ang nawalang buhay. Sana naman po, you try to consider that. Salamat po.\"', 'Others', 53, ''),
