(12411, '\"Please do consider our means on providing strong and possible internet connection so that we can seek to adjust on what are you talking about. If you think that way, then provide everything that we need or never the less just help us to lift on facing this modality of learning. Well we know that you have been a students during your time and no doubt you never encounter like this so you can say that. But please do some consideration on our side and most especially our parent\'s who can\'t provide what we need during this time hope you understand. Please do try to put your shoes on our shoes so you can understand us.\"', 'Sadness', 54, ''),
(12412, '\"Sana maisip niyo rin na kailangan ng student and teacher ng  kaunting pahinga and yung mga araw na inaasahan namin to rest eh tatanggalin niyo pa. HELLO! Hindi man kami pagod physically pero mentally wala na, sabog na. MAKISIMPATYA NAMAN KAYO SAMIN FOR ONCE , TRY NIYO ILAGAY YUNG SARILI NIYO SA SITWASYON NAMIN PARA MAINTINDIHAN NIYO YUNG STRUGGLES NAMING LAHAT. DUHHH (Just sayin)âœŒï¸\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
