(12509, '\"Greetings with peace!I am Romela Jane Anipot, 19 years old. I am a 2nd year college student taking up Bachelor in Secondary Education, Major in English at University of the Northern Philippines.I am humbly knocking from your kind hearts a small help as I try to raise funds in buying a laptop for my online class.Due to this anxiety-ridden pandemic, I was about to stop for this academic year due to financial matters and we can\'t afford to buy gadgets/electronics for my schooling since the mode of learning was shifted to the online class . My father is only helping his brother in farming while my mother is a housekeeper. I\'m considering myself as the eldest among with my two little sisters who are upcoming Grade 1 and Grade 4. This is because my loving brother passed away last August, 2019 due to an accident at the age of 19.Ever since I was in elementary, I am studying well and wanted to excel in class. In my senior high school life, I graduated with high honors/valedictorian. Honestly, \"', 'Sadness', 54, ''),
