(12567, '\"Ah yes, keep up the great work government !, we\'re just your disposable assets of of your cash and flesh for your people no wonder how the Philippines was netorared by its own spoiled government and its corrupted people, no wonder its the Philippines tho. Well  I guess its more fun in the philippines i say\"', 'Sadness', 54, ''),
(12568, '\"sir, baka akala nyo lahat ng studyante eh mayaman!!!!yung iba hirap sa internet,nagtatrabaho para mabuhay sana naman intindihin nyo rin sila wag puro mayaman ang intindihin nyo!!!!!\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12569, 'Welcome to another episode where thousands of students and teachers ask why the government is doing this at ang gobyerno ay nagtatanong kung bakit di umuunlad ang pilipinas.', 'Anger', 54, ''),
(12570, '\"this is the most stupidest bullshit I\'ve ever seen done, wtf are you talking about \"\"pag break, pinauuwi\"\", are you that fucking retarded, first of all a break is meant to help a student relax after an exam or even after schools, it isn\'t just meant for the student to go home, that part of your line obviously shows how mentally inept you are. second, even if they only meet for twice a week at minimum (which I doubt they actually do but you do you), the amount of Homeworks and performance task they can make up for all that lost time which they can also use to SELF STUDY, wow it\'s like that word doesn\'t exist for you to think students don\'t self study and need to always be in class to be productive. another thing, if you even use the excuse of \"\"yeah but look at us in the working class\"\" then I\'ve completely lost hope in you having a functioning brain, you guys get paid, we pay YOU to educate us, to remove breaks just because you don\'t get as much break time is the equivalent of an adult tak\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12571, 'hey! r u fucking kidding me? just a few weeks and we already need a break coz were fucking mentally and physically tired and yet? ur thinking or removing our only time to take a rest? u said that were already home? nope. like me. other students are living on a boarding house/apartments just to have a good internet connection before our home/location doesn\'t have any signal. our expenses is already doubled just to keep up with the previlaged. We need a break. Can\'t you see? are the government blind? We are fucking tired. U want to keep up with the other nations? then go and fucking migrate live on that fucking place. we don\'t need leaders who don\'t fucking care of it\'s people. We\'re all tired. aint eating a 3 times a day meal because we\'re saving money to live the next day. we still have expenses to pay. wake up man.', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12572, '\"Hoy, kami nga module para 24 hours ang activity namin for 10 subjects... maawa ka nman\"', 'Anger', 54, ''),
(12573, '\"sige lang po... ano pa? kami na rin ba mag hanap ng gamot sa covid? tutal hirap na hirap na kami itodo na natin. okay lang po sana kung bininigyan nyo kami ng paraan or supota para mapadali yung situation namin,pero wala naman po kaming natatanggap   \"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12574, 'Mamatay at masstress ang mga pag-asa ng bayan sa ginagawa nyo.', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12575, 'Nag open school namin pero kahit isang physical copy ng modules namin di pa ready tapos tambak pa yung sinesend na photo at  lessons na Naka doc at pdf format. Kahit twice lang magkita e May pinapagawa naman tapos May deadline agad', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12576, 'Grabe naman po yun wala manlang konsiderasyon sa emotional and mental state ng students? Please wag naman kayong magbulag bulagan sa mga hinanaing ng studyante', 'Sadness', 54, ''),
(12577, 'Sa\'min nga online class pero need pa din pumunta punta sa School every other week. Paano naman kaming mga independent dito sa Manila? We are already at home nga ba talaga?', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12578, '\"grabe na sd ni, bisan Christmas breaks ipagkait sa amoa. permente nlng gani ta gaatubang sa laptop og cp plus naa pai household chores na gabuhaton tas wala pa gali mi ka adjust ani nga new normal kai kami tnn lahi2 og pamaagi para makaapil aning online classes. haayst, wala na gali tai gakatun an kai puro ra requirements. we\'re  mentally and physically unstable na jdâ€â™€ï¸\"', 'Anger', 54, ''),
(12579, 'What the #/%_â‚¬ are you talking about. Give this kids a break. They need relaxation also ... grrrrr', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
(12580, '\"Hindi lahat ng estudyante 2-3 ung meet sa isang week ,wag ninyong i generalized. Paano naman ung ibang student na Monday to Friday ung meet ano??be flexible nalang?? Tanggalin ung summer at Christmas break kasi nasa bahay Lang Naman. Wow what a great REASON, paano naman ung kalusugan namin?!? Need din naming magpahinga Lalo n ung Mata dahil babad sa gadgets!!.Hindi porket nasa bahay kami Hindi na kami napapagod, Mas nakakastress.\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
(12581, '\"This is too much...Maybe they think we are doing nothing in our homes during our online classes. We have a lot to lose too, we are struggling too. So are you saying instructors are not allowed to rest during the breaks too? Are you prepared budget wise?\"', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
(12582, 'Are they assuming that we are on break all the time because we are at home? What kind of logic is that?', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
