(12596, '\"I thought you would help us? Its like your killing us!!! Do not focus on one side only sir, be open minded. Try understand the situation of the students. Anong 2x lang mag meet?? Sureee oiee. Di lang poh isa subjects namin. Isa pa poh, include those students na walang internet con. Sa lugar nila, na need pa nila hahanap nang lugar kung saan may inter con. Dios koh.. Don\'t be one sided naman.\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
