(12634, 'Wala na ngang pahinga mga estudyante pati sabado at linggo aalisin pa ang breaks? Wow ha?!!!', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
(12635, '\"It\'s not just about \"\"the students have to go home\"\". It\'s also about \"\"the students have to take a break\"\". So I think, hindi naman valid yung reason na nasa bahay na ang mga estudyante kaya di na kailangan ng students\' break. Kailangan din namin ng pahinga from the stressful schoolworks. And take note, mas nakakastress ngayon ang educational system. Online class pa nga. HA HA. Think about it.\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
(12636, 'BAT BA GANTO SISTEMA NG PINAS? Ewan ko ba pero ambobo ng ganto. Bat ba feeling nila same tayo with other countries? Nakaka pota', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12637, '\"I wish that president duterte, Ched, And Deped see this comment and agree with my decisions.. pls stop making fun of us we the students... Pls stop comparing Philippines to another country... Another country like USA has a fast wifi, discipline people, smart people, and active people, hindi kami mga amerikano, chinese, o anuman yan!! PILIPINO KAMI TAYO! Pls stop making fun of us just for money!! Sana one day Karmahin kayo (not you pres. duterte) Nakakapandilim kayo ng mata! May anak ba kayo? ginawa nyo naman kaming robot for just this fcking online class? What all I can say is MGA BULLSHIT KAYO DEPED AT CHED hindi ako natatakot sa inyo bakit? Diyos ba kayo para katakutan? May kapangyarihan ba kayo para katakutan? ha deped at ched? May pera lang kayo thats all you have!!! But Brain? Wala?! oh What a Fool and Bullshit we all students are sacrificing our time, our health, our lifestyle, our time of eating.. Lahat ng yan nakalimutan na namin because of this Godsake online class? tas sasabi\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12638, '\"Kelan magigising ang mga nasa itaas? Aantayin nyo na maubos lahat ng istudyante ? Grabe na ang ginagawa nyo! Siguro Wala kayong mga anak, apo, kamag anak na nag aaral kaya ang lakas ng loob nyo sabihin yan. Hindi nyo din inisip mga teachers/instructors na kelangan din umuwi sa pamilya nila !!!!\"', 'Anger', 54, ''),
