(12654, '\"This cannot help students and also parents.We should consider our time and bond with our family especially this season of Christmas,because life is too short.Open up you hearts and mind Ched because students or I should say many students are suffering with this kind of policies, they are committing suicide due to stress and anxiety attacks also teachers,guardian or parents can be stress because imstead of buying the money for their food they use the money on load.This kind of policies canâ€™t prepare us in the future.\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
(12655, 'So tuloy2 na ganun?luh... wala man lang pahinga sir... need din namin yan we are not imortal... plz.', 'Upset', 54, ''),
(12656, 'Hoyyy! wa ba ma kahibawo kung pila ka module ila ihatag sa amo ha??? NAA PAY MGA ACTIVITIES na performance based! Unsaon namo na ha? Tapos ang deadline 1week ihatag after ipasa ang moduless? HA? TUBAG!? Dili bana burden sa inyo!? nabuang mo! mga trabahoon sa balay dili nami makahimo!', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
(12657, '\"Not all universities are considerate. Instead na \'yung deadline pa is September 22, this professor told to his students, \"\"Lahat deadline na mamayang 5 pm (Sept 7) WALA NAMAN KAYONG GINAGAWA!\"\" So? Ano \'yun? Siya lang subject nila? Tanggap ko pa yun kung major yung subject which is hindi naman. Such a disappointment. \'Wag kayong magrereklamo kung in due time, bumaba ratings ng board passers and top notchers. Mulat naman yung dalawang mata niyo, may salamin pa, ba\'t nagbubulag-bulagan parin? Maayos naman \'yung pandinig niyo, Sumisigaw na nga kami, bakit \'di niyo naririnig? Halatang hindi para makapagturo yung goal niyo, nasa sasahudin. School is for learning, not for business mga, Ma\'am/Sir.\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(12658, 'Ang tanga naman mag isip..wala kaseng natututunan na bago. You think getting rid of school breaks helps students be more focused in learning and studying? Para mo na rin sinabi sa mga taong ngttrabaho na huwag magtake ng annual leaves or holiday leaves to be morw productive. My goodness. Sayang tax ng mga tao sayo.', 'Others', 54, ''),
