(12735, '\"Do you want to kill the students? First of all you allowed to open the classes for this year without having a proper and effective plan. You didn\'t even conduct a survey among the students and parents if they are agree with this. Students are the one who will study and face the struggles with this kind of system, not you. Every person need to rest, need to breathe. Even if they are just sitting or sleeping the whole day, week or even months. Wake up! THEY are NOT ROBOT!  Do you even know that because of this kind of system many students are having a hard time and even facing an anxiety? Please, don\'t be deaf. Listen to their voice. Listen to their reason and demand. Don\'t make decision without asking them. Because they are the one who\'s experiencing it, not you. BE CONSIDERATE. #AcademicFreeze\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
