(12904, '\"Ay HAHAHAHHAHAHAH So is he saying that We don\'t need breaks just because we already study in our respective houses?  Luh is that a joke? Kasi as far as I remember studying in our homes doesn\'t make us a ROBOT. We\'re still HUMANS who\'ll always need a break not only in our academic life but generally in EVERYTHING. Naka amnesia ba ang quarantine mga sis? Did he forgot that we still have life outside school? Like being a daughter and all? Did he also forgot that it also affects our mental health? Or maybe what he\'s trying to say is Let us all continue stuDYING since learning and education is so momentus than everything and that includes our family, personal time, mental health  and life.  So let us all stop complaining and just study then die, since at the end of the day we\'re still going to die anyway. That\'s why I suggest na we better study hard nalang mga sis, atleast we\'ve study as hard as we can before we go to heaven as if we can use it as an excuse just to enter there\"', 'Anger', 54, ''),
