(12932, '\"We, the educators, are also struggling so much. We\'ve been stressed so much especially if the institution we are in is also giving us a hard time in the midst of pandemic. We sometimes forget to eat on time, sleep on time and relax. We sacrificed a lot just so our compensation will be \"\"Justified\"\". Ergo, I miss the \"\"real normal\"\".\"', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
(12933, 'Hayop kayo. Hirap na hirap na ako sa pa online class ninyo tas hahabaan niyo pa. Pinupursige ko na nga matapos to gusto niyo ata tuloy tuloy na hanggang next year!!!', 'Annoyed', 54, ''),
