(12956, '\"ANO AKALA NIYO SA AMIN HINDI NAPAPAGOD? AKALA NIYO HINDI KAMI NAHIHIRAPAN SA KATARANTADUHAN NIYO? You never know how tired we are because you dont know what it feels! You have the audacity to change the schedule even if it means removing the christmas break and summer break! Are you really this desperate? even you all know that we are damn tired to all of your shit! You never listen to our voices! At kapal ng mukha niyong magbago ng mga karapatan namin? Galit na galit ako kasi wala kayong alam? Wala kayong alam sa dinadanas naming hirap na kagagawan niyo! Well to tell you honestly EVERYDAY may ginagawa kami! Tatlong araw sa zoom apat na araw sa paggawa ng sandamakmak na kaputa putahang activities na wala naman kaming natutunan! Who told you na twice a week lang? Ung iba yes pero kami araw araw! Anxiety, stress, depression, mental health, mental breakdown! Lahat yun naranasan na ng students wala kasi kayo alam kaya napakadali para sainyo magdecide. Wala kayong kwenta.\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
