(13127, '\"Is this a big joke? We\'re a student not a robot.\"\"Kasi nga, flexible ka. Hindi ka naman every day, 8-9 a-attend ng klase. Yung iba, twice a week lang magme-meet because everything now is done on a flexible manner,\"\"Sa totoo lang 8:00 am to 4:00 pm schedule namin every day, kahit sabihin pang twice a week lang mag me-meet how about the activities and assignments EVERY SUBJECTS sabihin na natin 2 activities every lesson per sub WITH DEADLINES. And ganto ang update???!You\'re not even focusing on the students who committed suicide about online classes eh, gusto niyo pa atang madagdagan. LOL\"', 'Others', 54, ''),
(13128, '\"Grabe, wala talaga kayong pakialam sa mental health ng students nyo. Mas mahirap ang online class, kasi may mga problema sa bahay at school na nagkakasabay sabay. Nakakaloka na kayo CHED! Halatang wala kayong pakialam samin.\"', 'Upset', 54, ''),
(13129, '\"empathy. ched. pakiayos ng desisyon sa buhay, pls. no breaks? what are we then? robot? wala na nga akong say bout sa academic freeze tapos ano na naman \'to?  ask ko lang, nag-conduct ba kayo ng study ukol dito?again. read. this \"\"I suggest those who are proposing any change in the academic policy, do a serious study, compute the cost, look at options, look at the parameters and submit it...\"\" De Vera said in a press conference.\"', 'Anger', 54, ''),
